text: Walter Delle Karth Sr. (12 August 1911 - 2004) was an Austrian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Austrian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Austria Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
